#. module: wechat_message_sale
#: model:wechat.message_templates,description:wechat_message_sale.wechat_message_template_sale_confirmation
msgid ""
"Sent to customers on order confirmation.\n"
"Please do the following in the background of WeChat official account:\n"
"1. \"Setting and development\" → \"official account setting\" → \"service category\";\n"
"2. Add \"Tools>Office\" to the service category;\n"
"3. \"Advertising Services and Services\" → \"Template Messages\" → \"Template Library\" → \"Category Template Library\", search for \"Sales Order Confirmed Notification\";\n"
"4. Add template with number \"59610\""
msgstr ""
"在订单确认时发送给客户。\n"
"请在微信公众号后台进行如下：\n"
"1. \"设置与开发\" → \"公众号设置\" → \"服务类目\";\n"
"2. 在服务类目中添加\"工具 > 办公\";\n"
"3. \"广告服与务\" → \"模板消息\" → \"模板库\" → \"类目模板库\"，搜索\"销售订单已确认通知\";\n"
"4. 添加编号为\"59610\"的模板"

#. module: wechat_message_sale
#: model:wechat.message_templates,description:wechat_message_sale.wechat_message_template_sale_cancellation
msgid ""
"Sent to customers when you cancel an order.\n"
"Please do the following in the background of WeChat official account:\n"
"1. \"Setting and development\" → \"official account setting\" → \"service category\";\n"
"2. Add \"Tools>Office\" to the service category;\n"
"3. \"Advertising Services and Services\" → \"Template Messages\" → \"Template Library\" → \"Category Template Library\", search for \"Sales order cancelled notification\";\n"
"4. Add template with number \"59611\""
msgstr ""
"在订单取消时发送给客户。\n"
"请在微信公众号后台进行如下：\n"
"1. \"设置与开发\" → \"公众号设置\" → \"服务类目\";\n"
"2. 在服务类目中添加\"工具 > 办公\";\n"
"3. \"广告服与务\" → \"模板消息\" → \"模板库\" → \"类目模板库\"，搜索\"销售订单已取消通知\";\n"
"4. 添加编号为\"59611\"的模板"

